message:
All of us must help beat the scourge of human trafficking. Here’s what you can do.
Talking to your children or younger family members about the issue can educate them and help keep them out of harm’s way.

data.description: Advocates, police and others offer solutions to the human trafficking problem and tell how to recognize sex trafficking threats and keep kids safe.
data.title: All of us must help beat the scourge of human trafficking. Here’s what you can do
